            <li>Empower African youths to be free innovative thinkers.</li>
            <li>Educate and train the youths on the importance of self independence with standard core values and self - confidence towards realising their potentials.</li>
            <li>Coaching/ teaching African youths to be selfless to their society.</li>
            <li>Modeling young African minds to be creative thinkers and highly dependable in the capital market.</li>
            <li>Sourcing for scholarships and sponsorships for the indigent intelligensias across Africa.</li>
